  "detailed_description": "<p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3500080/extras/3577592d2a58254c98ab8cad0229b8ea.avif?t=1768588678\" alt=\"\"width=800 height=356 /></span></p><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" ><strong>A CASUAL LOVELY MEMORY GAME</strong></h2><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><i><strong>Find My Love</strong></i> is a beautiful memory game where you must find lovely couples. Different from conventional memory games which you must find two same cards, in this game <strong>no card is equal to anyother.</strong> Find <i>the King and Queen, the Prince and Princess, the Cowboy and Cowgirl, the Groom and Bride...</i> and many other couples that truly loves each other. But be careful, there is some bad cards on table! Dont let any evil ideology destroy the pretty love of these couples, find each couple and help then to stay together until death do them part.</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >If you want play without any worries about flipping the <i>bad</i> cards, you can play in <strong>Relax Mode,</strong> in this mode there is no <i>bad card</i> on table, you will never lose. Just relax, enjoy the beautiful music and find the couples.</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >This is the first game of <strong>Araujo Castle.</strong> We created beautiful art and a loving atmosphere for you enjoy, relax and have fun while playing <strong>Find My Love.</strong></p><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" ><i><strong>FEATURES:</strong></i></h2><ul class=\"bb_ul\"><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Beautiful images  in anime style.</p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >24 beautiful backgrounds.</p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Beautiful, happy, relaxing and lovely background musics.</p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><strong>53 cards </strong>in total. 24 male cards, 24 female cards and 5 <i>bad card</i>s.</p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><strong>Relax Mode:</strong> No <i>bad card</i> on table, just relax and find the couples.</p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><strong>24 levels</strong> in normal mode. Each level more harder than the previous level, with more cards on table. Can you win all?</p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><strong>24 levels in Relax Mode.</strong> Each level with one couple more to be found.</p></li></ul><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" >Find lovely couples:</h2><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >You will enjoy searching for them.</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3500080/extras/78f522a918e0543644cd9db9c83a8cea.poster.avif?t=1768588678\" aria-label=\"Find couples that matches each other\" width=560 height=248 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3500080/extras/78f522a918e0543644cd9db9c83a8cea.webm?t=1768588678\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3500080/extras/78f522a918e0543644cd9db9c83a8cea.mp4?t=1768588678\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" >Don´t find the bad cards:</h2><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Take care!</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3500080/extras/9b087069f5c19415850d0a3824993c44.poster.avif?t=1768588678\" aria-label=\"Take care to not flip the bad cards\" width=560 height=248 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3500080/extras/9b087069f5c19415850d0a3824993c44.webm?t=1768588678\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3500080/extras/9b087069f5c19415850d0a3824993c44.mp4?t=1768588678\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span></p><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" >Romantic Atmosphere:</h2><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >You will fall in love for sure!</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3500080/extras/efb247d8b77e4ae57a6f215e962e0cff.avif?t=1768588678\" alt=\"Many couples to be found\" width=800 height=356 /></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" >A lot of cards to find:</h2><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Find All!</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3500080/extras/7df355e397a79c36650967438190b97d.avif?t=1768588678\" alt=\"\"width=800 height=356 /></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" >Beautiful Backgrounds:</h2><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >If has love, any place can be romantic.</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3500080/extras/0b540acdf6eeca6030560910f41ccef4.avif?t=1768588678\" alt=\"Find My Loe has beautiful backgrounds\" width=800 height=356 /></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Enjoy!</p>",
